data.description: This adorable, renovated, 2 bedroom 1 bath home is only missing you!! Huge fenced in yard and tons of parking! Great workshop in the basement, and covered front porch to sit and drink your morning coffee! Gutters, vinyl siding, and heat/air unit only 1 year old! Flooring, water heater, and all electrical 5 years old. Appliances only 4 years old and roof only 6 years old!! New plumbing! This is move-in ready and will not last long! No city taxes! Conveniently located to Rocky Top, Clinton, and the interstate. Call today to schedule your private showing!
